验证命令**: `pytest tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py -v`\n245: \n246: ---\n247: \n248: ## Phase 18: 集成测试\n249: \n250: - [ ] **T18.1** 验证完整 pack -> build -> publish 流程\n251: - [ ] **T18.2** 验证 invoke -> status 流程\n252: - [ ] **T18.3** 验证错误恢复流程\n253: - [ ] **T18.4** 验证并发操作\n254: \n255: **验证命令**: `pytest tests/ -k \"integration\" -v`\n256: \n257: ---\n258: \n259: ## Phase 19: 回归测试\n260: \n261: - [ ] **T19.1** 确保现有测试全部通过\n262: - [ ] **T19.2** 运行 pytest --tb=short\n263: - [ ] **T19.3** 验证测试覆盖率\n264: \n265: **验证命令**: `pytest tests/ --tb=short -v`\n266: \n267: ---\n268: \n269: ## 依赖关系\n270: \n271: ```\n272: Phase 1 (T1) → Phase 2 (T2)\n273: Phase 1 (T1) → Phase 3 (T3)\n274: Phase 3 (T3) → Phase 4 (T4)\n275: Phase 4 (T4) → Phase 5 (T5)\n276: Phase 5 (T5) → Phase 6-7 (T6-T7)\n277: Phase 3 (T3) → Phase 8 (T8)\n278: Phase 8 (T8) → Phase 9 (T9)\n279: Phase 9 (T9) → Phase 10-11 (T10-T11)\n280: Phase 1 (T1) → Phase 12-13 (T12-T13)\n281: Phase 12 (T12) → Phase 14-17 (T14-T17)\n282: Phase 14-17 → Phase 18 (集成测试)\n283: 所有 Phase → Phase 19 (回归测试)\n284: ```\n285: \n286: **并行执行**: Phase 4-17 可以并行执行 (独立模块)\n287: \n288: ---\n289: \n290: ## 验收标准\n291: \n292: - [ ] 所有测试通过 (pytest 0 failures)\n293: - [ ] 测试覆盖核心 SDK 功能 > 80%\n294: - [ ] 集成测试验证端到端流程\n295: - [ ] CLI 所有命令帮助信息完整\n296: - [ ] 错误处理覆盖边界情况\n297: - [ ] Mock 使用正确，不依赖外部服务\n298: \n299: ---\n300: \n301: ## 验证命令\n302: \n303: ```bash\n304: # 运行所有测试\n305: pytest tests/ -v\n306: \n307: # 运行特定测试文件\n308: pytest tests/test_cli.py tests/test_pack_runtime.py -v\n309: \n310: # 运行测试并显示覆盖率\n311: pytest tests/ --cov=agentcube --cov-report=term-missing\n312: \n313: # 运行测试并显示详细输出\n314: pytest tests/ -vv --tb=long\n315: \n316: # 只运行失败的测试\n317: pytest tests/ --lf\n318: ```\n\n(End of file - total 318 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-040 — Python SDK/CLI 测试\n\n**Module**: sdk-python/tests  \n**Language**: Python  \n**Size**: M  \n**Design**: [Stage ST-3 completed]\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: 异常模块测试\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** 验证 AgentCubeError 基类异常正确抛出\n- [ ] **T1.2** 验证 CommandExecutionError 包含 exit_code, stderr, command 属性\n- [ ] **T1.3** 验证 CommandExecutionError 继承自 AgentCubeError\n- [ ] **T1.4** 验证 SessionError 继承自 AgentCubeError\n- [ ] **T1.5** 验证 DataPlaneError 继承自 AgentCubeError\n\n**验证命令**: `pytest tests/test_exceptions.py -v`\n\n---","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-040/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775884423048,"end":1775884423071}}}}
